<section class="flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-24 md:py-0 md:min-h-screen container mx-auto">
    <div class="w-full">
        <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="scroll-animate text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent-color">The Process</h2>
            <p class="scroll-animate delay-100 mt-3 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-serif text-text-color">Engage with Intention</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-16 w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto timeline-container">
            <div class="space-y-12 md:space-y-16">

                
                <div class="scroll-animate how-it-works-step flex justify-center md:justify-start">
                    <div class="relative md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 text-center md:text-left">
                        <div class="how-it-works-dot hidden md:block right-0 translate-x-1/2"></div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold">1. The Proposition</h3>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600">Begin by using the `/debate` command. Clearly state the motion you wish to discuss and challenge a fellow member of the community to engage.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                
                <div class="scroll-animate delay-100 how-it-works-step flex justify-center md:justify-end">
                    <div class="relative md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 text-center md:text-right">
                        <div class="how-it-works-dot hidden md:block left-0 -translate-x-1/2"></div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold">2. The Discourse</h3>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600">The bot establishes the rules of engagement. Participants present their arguments within timed rounds, ensuring a structured and equitable exchange of ideas.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                
                <div class="scroll-animate delay-200 how-it-works-step flex justify-center md:justify-start">
                     <div class="relative md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 text-center md:text-left">
                        <div class="how-it-works-dot hidden md:block right-0 translate-x-1/2"></div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold">3. The Verdict</h3>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600">Upon conclusion, the community casts their votes for the most persuasive argument. Victory contributes to your Elo rating, marking your ascent on the server's leaderboard.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
